subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Jeff Overton shot a three-under-par 69 to take a one-shot lead over Tag Ridings (68) in the Turning Stone Resort Championship in Verona, N.Y. Playing through wind, rain and a brief shower of hail, Overton was at eight-under 136.
